                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.0144/162: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Chihuahua</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stewart</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chihuahua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-09-03T10:00:00-07:04">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 3, 1919, 10 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received 4.45 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>For the second time within a week two American air planes flew over Chihuahua
                    September 2, 4 p.m. causing deep resentment but so far no demonstration. Embassy
                    advised.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stewart</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
